dct_title_s: New South Wales, eastern coast of Terra Australis or New Holland
dct_alternative_sm: Eastern coast of Terra Australis or New Holland
dct_description_sm: drawn & engraved by J. & C. Walker.
Map of eastern coast of New South Wales from Port Macquarie in the north to Bateman's Bay in the south showing towns, rivers and counties. Relief shown by hachures.
Imprint on map: Published by Cochrane & Co. Waterloo Place April 1835.
In upper margin: For Montgomery Martin's History of the British colonies, Vol. IV, Africa & Australia.
Plate from volume 4 of: History of the British colonies / R. Montgomery R. Martin R. London : J. Cochrane, 1834-1835.
Also available in an electronic version via the internet at: http://nla.gov.au/nla.map-rm4150.
